      <title>彭博英国民意调查：工党支持率下滑但保持领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-labour-slips-while-keeping-big-lead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社英国民意调查显示，工党领袖基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 谨慎的选举策略似乎取得了成效，距离投票日仅剩三天，反对党仍领先首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的执政党保守党 20 个百分点以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-labour-slips-while-keeping-big-lead</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
